* angle restraint using CHARMM MMFP
* using with CHARMM or DOMDEC


MMFP
GEO sphere angle -
     harmonic symmetric force 80.0 tref 112 dtoff 0.0 -
     select resname LIG .and. type C10 end -
     select segid PROT .and. resid 173 .and. type OG end -
     select segid PROT .and. resid 41 .and. type NE2 end
GEO PRINT
END
